{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"eab19ccd-52a2-47b5-b895-bbc80f8c44ef","content":"Yes, you'll hit **framework compatibility issues**. MSTest v3 dropped support for several older TFMs. Here's the breakdown for your targets:\n\n| Target Framework | MSTest v3 Support |\n|---|---|\n| `net462` | ✅ Supported |\n| `netcoreapp3.1` | ❌ **Dropped** |\n| `net5.0` | ❌ **Dropped** |\n\nMSTest v3 requires **.NET 6.0+** (for .NET Core/modern .NET) and **.NET Framework 4.6.2+** (still supported).\n\n**To migrate, you'd need to:**\n1. Replace `net5.0` → `net6.0` (or later) and drop `netcoreapp3.1`.\n2. Replace the two separate packages with the unified `MSTest` meta-package:\n   ```xml\n   <PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"3.x.x\" />\n   ```\n3. Review any deprecated API usage (e.g., some assert overloads changed).\n\nWould you like me to update the project file?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"3307b401-4c87-49c6-aa6c-fc68029c84a2","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a project that multi-targets `net5.0`, `net462`, and `netcoreapp3.1`. They want to migrate from MSTest v2 (2.2.10) to MSTest v3.\n\nMSTest v3 dropped support for older target frameworks. Let me provide the key compatibility issues:\n\n1. **MSTest v3 dropped support for .NET Framework < 4.6.2** — but they have `net462` which is .NET Framework 4.6.2, so that should be fine.\n2. **MSTest v3 dropped support for .NET Core 3.1** — `netcoreapp3.1` is no longer supported.\n\n\n3. **MSTest v3 dropped support for .NET 5.0** — `net5.0` is also no longer supported.\n\nSo both `net5.0` and `netcoreapp3.1` are problematic. MSTest v3 only supports .NET 6.0+ and .NET Framework 4.6.2+. Beyond the framework compatibility issues, MSTest v3 also consolidated its packaging into a single `MSTest` meta-package instead of separate `MSTest.TestFramework` and `MSTest.TestAdapter` packages, and some APIs were removed or changed. The main blocker here is that `netcoreapp3.1` and `net5.0` are no longer supported at all.","outputTokens":626,"requestId":"67CF:CA1D0:3082ACA:35B40E1:69FD5067"},"id":"daa1265f-e37f-463b-a16e-d079811fb11e","timestamp":"2026-05-08T02:54:43.478Z","parentId":"83294862-5ea8-4940-83eb-2664bd4323fd"}
